HAVE SOME SEX WITH ME.

18:21.800 --> 18:23.633
- WHAT ARE YOU TALKING ABOUT?

18:23.633 --> 18:26.933
- OUR THING.
OUR NOT HAVING SEX THING.

18:26.933 --> 18:28.700
- ARE WE STILL DOING THAT?

18:32.533 --> 18:34.367
- OF COURSE
WE'RE STILL DOING IT.

18:34.367 --> 18:35.967
IT'S BEEN 26 DAYS
OF DOING IT--

18:35.967 --> 18:37.567
NOT DOING IT.

18:37.567 --> 18:40.733
- I'M SORRY.
I TOTALLY FORGOT.

18:42.800 --> 18:44.233
- YEAH, RIGHT.

18:44.233 --> 18:45.600
- I MEAN, I CAN'T BELIEVE IT,

18:45.600 --> 18:47.700
BUT REALLY,
I TOTALLY FORGOT.

18:47.700 --> 18:49.233
- PLEASE.

18:49.233 --> 18:51.633
YOU EXPECT ME TO BELIEVE THAT
YOU DIDN'T REALIZE THAT WE--

18:51.633 --> 18:55.067
WE WENT 26 DAYS
WITHOUT HAVING SEX?

18:57.800 --> 18:59.767
- IT'S JUST,
I'VE BEEN REALLY BUSY.

18:59.767 --> 19:02.500
YOU KNOW, THE PTA FUND-RAISER
IS COMING UP,

19:02.500 --> 19:06.433
AND I'VE JUST HAD
A LOT ON MY MIND.

19:10.700 --> 19:13.900
- 26 DAYS.

19:13.900 --> 19:17.733
YOU WEREN'T EVEN TRYING.

19:17.733 --> 19:21.733
GUESS I WAS NEVER REALLY CLOSE
TO HAVIN' THE POWER, WAS I?

19:21.733 --> 19:23.533
- SORRY.

19:25.467 --> 19:28.333
- ALL THIS TIME,
I-I THOUGHT YOU WERE DOIN'

19:28.333 --> 19:30.700
