TO TORTURE ME.

19:30.700 --> 19:32.067
- WHAT THINGS?

19:32.067 --> 19:34.533
- FORGET IT.

19:34.533 --> 19:36.067
- NO, COME ON.

19:36.067 --> 19:37.700
- YOU KNOW.

19:37.700 --> 19:38.867
LIKE BITE YOUR LOWER LIP

19:38.867 --> 19:40.800
WHEN YOU USE THE REMOTE
TO CHANGE THE CHANNEL.

19:40.800 --> 19:43.567
- I DO THAT?
- YEAH!

19:43.567 --> 19:45.267
OR HOW ABOUT
WHEN YOU KEEP ONE OF YOUR LEGS

19:45.267 --> 19:48.433
OUTSIDE OF THE COVERS
AND THE PAJAMA RIDES UP IT?

19:48.433 --> 19:50.500
- IT'S JUST BECAUSE I'M HOT.

19:50.500 --> 19:53.600
- YES, YOU ARE!

19:53.600 --> 19:55.367
EVEN WHEN YOU SLEEP,
EVERY SO OFTEN,

19:55.367 --> 19:57.800
YOU KIND OF SIGH A LITTLE.

19:57.800 --> 20:00.367
[sighs quietly]

20:00.367 --> 20:02.367
- YOU HAVEN'T
SLEPT MUCH LATELY, HAVE YOU?

20:02.367 --> 20:05.533
- NO.

20:05.533 --> 20:07.033
EVEN NOW.

20:07.033 --> 20:08.767
LOOK AT YOU.

20:08.767 --> 20:11.033
