20:13.700 --> 20:15.600
ROBE.

20:17.033 --> 20:19.900
- I'M A MESS.

20:19.900 --> 20:23.100
- YEAH, WELL, I GUESS
EVEN WHEN YOU'RE NOT TRYIN',

20:23.100 --> 20:25.000
IT STILL WORKS.

20:31.167 --> 20:32.800
- WHAT? WHAT ARE YOU DOIN'?

20:32.800 --> 20:35.633
- YOU JUST GOT
