20:35.633 --> 20:38.167
- [laughs]

20:38.167 --> 20:40.933
WHOA, WHOA, WAIT, WAIT.

20:40.933 --> 20:44.000
ARE YOU TOYING WITH ME?

20:44.000 --> 20:45.500
