START TO CRY.

20:50.567 --> 20:52.900
- I'VE BEEN WAITING FOR THIS
FOR A LONG TIME, TOO, RAY.

20:52.900 --> 20:56.733
AND BY THE WAY,
IT'S BEEN 27 DAYS, NOT 26.

20:56.733 --> 21:03.067
- AH, YOU DO RE--

21:03.067 --> 21:04.867
